135:                                            + " <li><code>acks=all</code> This means the leader will wait for the full set of in-sync replicas to"
136:                                            + " acknowledge the record. This guarantees that the record will not be lost as long as at least one in-sync replica"
137:                                            + " remains alive. This is the strongest available guarantee. This is equivalent to the acks=-1 setting."
